column5: Im pretty sure it's the effexor. I was on it and it took my high away.
Thank you for this amazing article. It is saved and bookmarked. Very much needed.

I'm going through this right now and it's annoying. So yesterday I decided not to text anything just to see if he would text me. Got a text at 11 something that night asking how my day went. I did respond. That kind of settled my nerves so I sent a text this morning...still nothing. I'm not sure what to think or if I'm being too emotional.
Yeah I'm thinking of weaning off the effexor, I miss my high.
Effexor took my high away, so fustrating.
I desperately need a plug. In kc as well
Anyone ever try leafedin? I'm desperate for a reliable plug since mine moved out of state.
